Food Extrusion names chief executive . Food Extrusion Inc Tuesday said it appointed Allen Simon as chief executive officer on April 14 . Simon joins Food Extrusion from Shaklee U . S . Inc , a manufacturer and marketer of nutritional and personal care products , where he worked for 12 years . Simon replaces Dan McPeak as chief executive . McPeak remains as chairman of the board and will concentrate on developing the business . " Allen Simon is the quality executive we have been seeking to lead our company to rapid domestic and international expansion , " McPeak said in a statement . " He is uniquely qualified to develop our growth strategy since he has done it before in a strikingly similar situation . " 
